    dc:creator "Pogonoski, John J.; Gon, Ofer; Appleyard, Sharon A." ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Redescription and distributional range extension of the Speckled Siphonfish, Siphamia guttulata (Pisces: Apogonidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3763513>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3763509>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3763511>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3763517>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3763515> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3763513>
    dc:description "FIGURE­3.­Median predorsal scales of Siphamia guttulata (A—paralectotype, AMS I.16306-001, 25.7 mm SL; B—CSIRO H 7457-01, 27 mm SL) and Siphamia tubifer (C—CSIRO H 6752-02, 31 mm SL). Scale bar = 0.5 mm. Yellow arrows point to first dorsal spine, numbers or pink arrows indicate median predorsal scales. Fifth median predorsal scale of Fig. C is a scale pocket as the scale has been lost." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3763513/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3763509>
    dc:description "FIGURE­1. Lateral view of Siphamia guttulata (CSIRO H 6930-02, 25 mm SL). Scale bar = 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3763509/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3763511>
    dc:description "FIGURE­2. Digital radiograph of Siphamia guttulata (CSIRO H 6648-02, 25 mm SL). Blue circle highlighting two supraneurals. Scale bar = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3763511/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3763517>
    dc:description "FIGURE­5. Maximum likelihood tree based on the Kimura 2-parameter model of the COI sequences from the Siphamia species with P. kauderni as the outgroup. Tree shown here has the highest log likelihood following 10 000 replications. The percentage of trees in which the associated taxa clustered together is shown next to the branches, branch lengths are measured in the number of substitutions per site and all positions containing gaps and missing data have been eliminated." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3763517/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3763515>
    dc:description "FIGURE­4.­Map of selected records of Siphamia species recorded in Queensland and Papua New Guinea waters in 2003–2005, including the type locality of Siphamia guttulata. Some symbols represent more than one specimen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3763515/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

